00:23:48,890 --> 00:23:51,310
ved å treffe sin mellomromstasten en gang?

530
00:23:51,310 --> 00:23:52,692
>> PUBLIKUM: [uhørlig]

531
00:23:52,692 --> 00:23:54,150
DAVID J. MALAN: Ikke fullt så ille.

532
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:57,070
Bare én byte ganger en milliard.

533
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:57,871
så a--

534
00:23:57,871 --> 00:23:59,120
PUBLIKUM: 8 milliarder gigabyte.

535
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:00,370
DAVID J. MALAN: Ikke 8000000000.

