1058
00:48:38,800 --> 00:48:41,720
Og hashtag i denne sammenheng
bare betyr "unik identifikator."

1059
00:48:41,720 --> 00:48:43,750
Jeg vil ikke sette det i HTML-filen.

1060
00:48:43,750 --> 00:48:46,880
Jeg, over her, bare si
quote unquote "først."

1061
00:48:46,880 --> 00:48:48,470
>> Så la meg laste.

